This is the hardware list that run this sketch.

- Arduino Pro 3.3v ATmega328, 8Mhz.
- BLESerial2 (for BLE Connection with iPhone/Smartphone)
- Adafruit_SI1145 (for measuring UV Index)
- SparkFun TSL2561 (for measuring light (Lux))
- Adafruit BME280 (for measuring temperture, humidity and pressure)
- MPU9520 (for measuring motion of the sensor)

